Dependencies (SDL3 versions):
 SDL3
 SDL3_image
 SDL3_ttf
 SDL3_mixer
 CMake >= 3.16

On Ubuntu/Debian (once SDL3 packages are available in your distro, or built
from source):
 sudo apt-get install g++ cmake ninja-build

From the top directory (the one with CMakeLists.txt and the src/, graphics/,
fonts/, maps/, sound/ subdirs):

  cmake -B build -G Ninja
  cmake --build build
  ./build/roadfighter


